{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ddad6e968b","title":"毛泽东关于目前农村集体所有制形式问题的批语","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d5e36cd6de","index":0,"year":1958,"month":2,"day":28,"articleId":"ddad6e968b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"93505c00d9","type":"title","text":"毛泽东关于目前农村集体所有制形式问题的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ddad6e968b"},{"id":"5fe365219c","type":"paragraph","text":"此件印发各同志。政策是对的，理由没有说清楚。基本的队有制，部分的社有制，不但1958年是如此，1959年及往后几年还是如此。要翻过来，变为基本的社有、部分的队有制，需要多年时间，这是一个由小集体所有制(队有)到大集体所有制(社有)的逐步发展过程。不认识这个客观真理，不可能根本解决问题，不能说服人。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ddad6e968b"},{"id":"cf48e601d9","type":"paragraph","text":" 毛泽东1959年2月28日","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ddad6e968b"}],"page":{"id":"5154326e93","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"ddad6e968b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}